[[Image:Mocca.jpg|thumb|Logo of Mocca.com]]

'''Mocca.com''' is an online advertising service run by [[MediaCorp]]. Mocca stands for MediaCorp Online Communities and Classified Advertising.<ref>{{cite web | url = http://mocca.com/portal/site/CAS/menuitem.74fdd69321a7d5b046c4c2911e1000a0/?vgnextoid=f6e08d73d4822110VgnVCM100000e101000aRCRD | title = About Us | accessdaymonth = 27 November |accessyear=2007}}</ref> It is part of MediaCorp Online.

It has a slogan of "Search, Buy, Sell, Connect", allowing people to connect with other people in [[Singapore]] to advertise.

==Pricing plans==
For the first month or until further notice from its launch, all posting of advertisements on the website are free. The advertisements will be there for a duration of 14 days. It is still free for now,<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.channelnewsasia.com/stories/singaporelocalnews/view/290452/1/.html | title = MediaCorp launches interactive ad portal mocca.com | accessdate = 27 November 2007}}</ref><ref name="mocca.com">{{cite web | url = http://mocca.com/portal/site/CAS/menuitem.ef9c181e851b609ffe81ff651e1000a0/?vgnextoid=8178735d74461110VgnVCM100000e101000aRCRD | title = Price Plans | accessdaymonth = 27 November|accessyear= 2007}}</ref> after which the duration is shortened to 7 days and it will cost S$15.00.

There are three pricing plans as of current:<ref name="mocca.com" />
